歌曲获得的褒贬不一。许多评论家高度赞扬了阿黛尔的声乐部分，同时亦有评论家对歌曲给出批评。《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》编辑莉亚·格林布拉特（{{lang|en|Leah Greenblatt}}）称赞歌曲是一首为“遭到轻视的女性”写就的一首颂歌，称歌曲“鼓动翻涌着[[泰坦尼克号|泰坦尼克号]]一般宏大悲鸣的纯粹力量。”<ref name="ew">{{cite news|url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20464873,00.html|title=Review: Adele, 21|publisher=[[时代公司|Time]] division of [[Time_Warner|Time Warner]]|work=Entertainment Weekly|author=Greenblatt, Leah|date=2011-02-09|accessdate=2014-05-23|archive-date=2012-07-29|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69WfitlCU?url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20464873,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

音乐杂志《{{lang|en|No Ripcord}}》评论家加里·麦金利（{{lang|en|Gary McGinley}}）高度赞扬了这首歌，称之为《21》专辑中“最上口的一首歌”。<ref name="ripcord">{{cite news|url=http://www.noripcord.com/reviews/music/adele/21|title=Adele ''21''|publisher=No Ripcord|first=Gary|last=McGinley|date=25 January 2011|accessdate=2014-05-23|archive-date=2016-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160411090546/http://www.noripcord.com/reviews/music/adele/21|dead-url=no}}</ref>美国[[伊利诺伊州|伊利诺伊州]]《{{link-en|每日先驱报 (伊利诺伊州)|Daily Herald (Arlington Heights)|每日先驱报}}》称赞了阿黛尔在歌曲中“史诗一般的”声音。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.dailyherald.com/article/20110224/entlife/702249860/|title=Adele's second is personal and perfect|work=Daily Herald|publisher=Paddock Publications|date=24 February 2011|accessdate=2014-05-23|archive-date=2014-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140314205010/http://www.dailyherald.com/article/20110224/entlife/702249860/|dead-url=no}}</ref>音乐网站[[Consequence_of_Sound|Consequence of Sound]]编辑尼克·弗里德（{{lang|en|Nick Freed}}）则认为歌曲是阿黛尔“最强大、最开放”的作品。<ref name="Consequence of Sound" />他还称赞歌曲是“专辑中最愤怒的歌曲之一”，“副歌朗朗上口，在最后一次重复演唱时，阿黛尔彻底释放了内心受到的伤害和愤怒”，展现出了真实的情感。<ref name="Consequence of Sound" />娱乐网站[[Digital_Spy|Digital Spy]]评论家罗伯特·柯普西（{{lang|en|Robert Copsey}}）也赞扬了这首歌曲，称副歌“大胆而令人激动”，并评价阿黛尔“怒吼般的”演唱配合了“戏剧化的弦乐伴奏”，“恰到好处的爆发夺人心魄”，“经典而不俗套”。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/singlesreviews/a326001/adele-set-fire-to-the-rain.html|title=Adele: 'Set Fire to the Rain'|publisher=Digital Spy. Hachette Filipacchi Médias|date=2011-07-03|first=Robert|last=Copsey|accessdate=2014-05-24|archive-date=2013-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130703203320/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/singlesreviews/a326001/adele-set-fire-to-the-rain.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>娱乐网站PopCrush称赞歌曲是“缓解心碎的一剂良药”，“强大而愤怒”，与听众“分担着内心的痛苦”，而当歌曲结束时阿黛尔的声音正如“火焰舔舐着脚跟，热浪掠过每一寸肌肤”。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://popcrush.com/adele-set-fire-to-the-rain/|work=PopCrush|date=2011-11-09|title=<nowiki>Adele, ‘Set Fire to the Rain’ – Song Review</nowiki>|accessdate=2014-05-24|archive-date=2014-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140525200701/http://popcrush.com/adele-set-fire-to-the-rain/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

而亦有很多评论对歌曲提出批评。美国音乐杂志《{{link-en|URB (杂志)|URB (magazine)|URB}}》评论称这首歌“内容只适合[[星巴克|星巴克]]的风格”，更批评其“夸张滥情”。<ref name="urb">{{Cite news|url=http://www.urb.com/2011/02/25/adele-21/|title=Adele: ''21''|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131102030234/http://www.urb.com/2011/02/25/adele-21/|archivedate=2013-11-02|work=URB|date=25 February 2011|accessdate=2014-05-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref>《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》评论《21》专辑时批评这首歌是专辑中的“小败笔”，制作人弗雷泽·史密斯是“整个制作团队中思维受流行风格影响最大的成员”，其制作的声音效果“完全是多余”。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2011/03/01/arts/music/01choice.html?_r=1|title=New Music From Adele, Lucinda Williams and Cuong Vu|work=The New York Times|publisher=The New York Times Company|author=Caramanica, Jon; Pareles Jon; Chinene Nate|date=1 March 2011|accessdate=2014-05-23|archive-date=2011-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110731073014/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/03/01/arts/music/01choice.html?_r=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>英国音乐网站{{link-en|MusicOMH|MusicOMH}}评论家约翰·墨菲（{{lang|en|John Murphy}}）在对《21》的评论中提到这首歌，称这首歌虽然很有力量，但同时也给出负面评价，指出歌曲只是“中规中矩”，“制作过度”，是“专辑唯一的失败之处”。他表示，阿黛尔的声音最适合用简单的钢琴伴奏，过度制作反而喧宾夺主。<ref name="OMH">{{cite web |url=http://www.musicomh.com/reviews/albums/adele-21 |title=Adele: ''21'' Review |last1=Murphy |first1=John |date=2011-01-24 |publisher=musicOMH |accessdate=2014-05-21 |archive-date=2014-05-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140525213408/http://www.musicomh.com/reviews/albums/adele-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>澳大利亚《{{link-en|先驱太阳报|Herald Sun}}》撰稿人卡梅隆·亚当斯（{{lang|en|Camreon Adams}}）称歌曲只是“为下一支单曲做准备”，“副歌一响起便让人不想再听”。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.heraldsun.com.au/ipad/album-of-the-week-adele/story-fn6cc2fg-1225991191372|title=Album of the week: Adele|work=Herald Sun |location=Australia|publisher=The Herald and Weekly Times|first=Camreon|last=Adams|date=20 January 2011|accessdate=2014-05-23}}</ref>《[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]》评论家艾莉森·斯图尔特（{{lang|en|Allison Stewart}}）也批评歌曲，称其“[[合成器|合成]][[摇滚乐|摇滚]]的风格完全用错了地方”，“连阿黛尔也无法挽救”。<ref name=electro>{{cite news|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2011/02/21/AR2011022103780.html|title=Adele's '21' album: Sophomore disc designed to transcend trends|first=Allison|last=Stewart|date=21 February 2011|work=The Washington Post|publisher=[[华盛顿邮报公司|The Washington Post Company]]|accessdate=2014-05-23|archive-date=2014-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140606204618/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2011/02/21/AR2011022103780.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

阿黛尔演唱这首歌的现场版本收录于《{{link-en|皇家阿尔伯特音乐厅演唱会 (阿黛尔)|Live at the Royal Albert Hall (Adele video)|皇家阿尔伯特音乐厅演唱会}}》的DVD中，并获得了[[第55届格莱美奖|第55届格莱美奖]]的“最佳流行歌手表演”大奖。<ref name="grammy"/>

