==榜单排名及销量认证==
《以火焚雨》在欧洲大受欢迎，这首歌在[[奥地利|奥地利]]、[[丹麦|丹麦]]、[[芬兰|芬兰]]、[[法国|法国]]、[[德国|德国]]、[[爱尔兰|爱尔兰]]、[[意大利|意大利]]、[[挪威|挪威]]、[[瑞士|瑞士]]等国单曲排行榜中进入前十，在[[比利时|比利时]]、[[捷克|捷克]]、[[波兰|波兰]]、[[斯洛伐克|斯洛伐克]]和[[荷兰|荷兰]]等国甚至登上排行榜冠军。<ref name="aus" />这支单曲在[[英国单曲排行榜|英国单曲排行榜]]上首周排名第79位，<ref name="stats" />最高登上排行榜第11位，并在这一位置上保持了两周。<ref name="stats">{{cite web|url=http://www.chartstats.com/release.php?release=50201|title=Chart Stats – Adele – Set Fire to the Rain|publisher=Chart Stats. The Official Charts Company|accessdate=2014-05-23|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120722181310/http://www.chartstats.com/release.php?release=50201|archivedate=2012-07-22|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.musicweek.com/story.asp?sectioncode=1&storycode=1046070&c=1|title=The Wanted buck boy-band trend keep top spot on singles chart|first=Alan|last=Jones|date=24 July 2011|work=Music Week|publisher=Intent Media|accessdate=2014-05-23|archive-date=2015-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150703023623/http://www.musicweek.com/story.asp?sectioncode=1&storycode=1046070&c=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>而在美国，这首歌作为单曲正式发行之前已经三次进入[[告示牌百强单曲榜|告示牌百强单曲榜]]并在榜单内停留了6周，最高排名第72位。单曲正式发行后于2012年2月4日的榜单中登上了冠军位置并保持了两周。夺冠时这支单曲已经在排行榜中停留了不连续的21周。<ref>{{cite web |last=Molanphy |first=Chris |url=http://blogs.villagevoice.com/music/2012/01/adele_set_fire_to_the_rain_number_one_hot_100.php |title=100 & Single: Adele's Focus-Grouped Chart-Topper And The Demise Of The "Deep Cut" – New York Music – Sound of the City |publisher=Blogs.villagevoice.com |date=2012-01-30 |accessdate=2012-05-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120510033439/http://blogs.villagevoice.com/music/2012/01/adele_set_fire_to_the_rain_number_one_hot_100.php |archive-date=2012-05-10 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/chartbeat/509079/weekly-chart-notes-adele-kelly-clarkson-gavin-degraw |title=Weekly Chart Notes: Adele, Kelly Clarkson, Gavin DeGraw – Chart Beat |publisher=Billboard.com |date= |accessdate=2012-05-23 |archive-date=2013-05-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130528120051/http://www.billboard.com/articles/chartbeat/509079/weekly-chart-notes-adele-kelly-clarkson-gavin-degraw |dead-url=no }}</ref>这首歌成为阿黛尔《21》专辑中的连续第三支冠军单曲，而同时《21》在[[公告牌二百强专辑榜|公告牌二百强专辑榜]]中也获得冠军，阿黛尔也因此成为首个在专辑保持冠军位置的同时获得三支冠军单曲的艺人。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/509788/adeles-fire-burns-path-to-hot-100-summit|work=Billboard|title=Adele's 'Fire' Burns Path to Hot 100 Summit|publisher=Nielsen Business Media, Inc|first=Gary|last=Trust|date=25 January 2012|accessdate=2014-05-23|archive-date=2014-09-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140917074747/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/509788/adeles-fire-burns-path-to-hot-100-summit|dead-url=no}}</ref>

